cff-version: 1.2.0
title: Genomics Agent Workspace
message: >
  If you use this workspace or adapt it for your own projects,
  please cite it as below.
type: software
version: 0.2.0
date-released: "2025-06-24"
abstract: >
  A reproducible Claude Code workspace for genomics QC orchestration.
  Provides local fallback tools for BAM/VCF/ATAC-seq QC, pre-flight
  environment checks, reference validation, and biological interpretation
  guardrails. Designed to complement Anthropic Life Sciences skills
  and nf-core pipelines, not replace them.
keywords:
  - genomics
  - bioinformatics
  - claude-code
  - quality-control
  - reproducibility
  - single-cell
  - atac-seq
  - wgs
license: MIT
url: "https://github.com/vfferreira/genomics-agent-workspace"
